<template>
  <check-box></check-box>
</template>

<script>
import CheckBox from './components/CheckBox.vue';
export default {
  components: {
    CheckBox
  },
  data() {
    return {
      checkboxes: [],
    }
  },
  created() {
    fetchCheckBox().then(result => this.checkboxes = result.data)
  }
}
</script>
